    freenect_chunk_cb
    Typedef for stream chunk processing callbacks

    Holds information about the usb context.
    freenect_depth_cb
    Typedef for depth image received event callbacks
    freenect_device
    Holds device information.
    freenect_device_attributes
    A struct used in enumeration to give access to serial numbers, so you can open a particular device by serial rather than depending on index.
    freenect_frame_mode
    Structure to give information about the width, height, bitrate, framerate, and buffer size of a frame in a particular mode, as well as the total number of bytes needed to hold a single frame.
